<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title th:text="${title}">SkillUp</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="flex flex-1">

    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <div class="group relative w-16 hover:w-64 bg-blue-200 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col p-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2">
            <img th:src="@{/assets/Imagenes/LogoSkillup.png}" alt="SkillUp Logo" class="w-8 group-hover:w-10 transition-all" />
            <span class="text-gray-700 font-bold hidden group-hover:block">SKILLUP</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/lobby}" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-md">
                <span class="text-xl">🏠</span> <span class="hidden group-hover:block">Inicio</span>
            </a>
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/cursos}" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-md">
                <span class="text-xl">📚</span> <span class="hidden group-hover:block">Cursos</span>
            </a>
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/certificados}" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-md">
                <span class="text-xl">🎓</span> <span class="hidden group-hover:block">Certificados</span>
            </a>
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/foro}" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-md">
                <span class="text-xl">💬</span> <span class="hidden group-hover:block">Foro</span>
            </a>
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/soporte}" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-200 rounded-md">
                <span class="text-xl">⚙️</span> <span class="hidden group-hover:block">Soporte</span>
            </a>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENIDO -->
    <main class="flex-1 px-6 md:px-16 py-12 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">APRENDE SIN LÍMITES</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-800 text-lg">Potencia tus habilidades, mejora tu futuro con herramientas, cursos y apoyo académico diseñado para ti.</p>

                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-purple-600 text-xl">✔️</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Tareas calificadas</strong>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Reciba retroalimentación personalizada para mejorar continuamente.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class="text-purple-600 text-xl">✔️</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Asistencia académica</strong>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Asesoría inmediata de tutores y comunidad estudiantil.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <img th:src="@{/assets/Imagenes/Certificado.jpg}" alt="Certificado" class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Estadísticas -->
        <div class="mt-12 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 text-center gap-6">
            <div>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">+5,000</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Estudiantes activos</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">85%</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Del éxito profesional depende de habilidades blandas</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-700">98%</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Satisfacción estudiantil</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">¿Listo para comenzar?</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">Explora nuestros cursos y da el primer paso hacia tu futuro profesional.</p>
            <a th:href="@{/usuarios/cursos}" class="bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Explorar Cursos</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div th:replace="layouts/footer :: footer"></div>

</body>
</html>
